n<li>沪指收盘：3500 点  </li>\n<li>参与人数：66 人  </li>\n<li><code>3500 % 66 = 2</code> </li>\n<li>👉 2 楼中奖</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1772434880, "replies": 272, "id": 1195195}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_large.png?m=1588961795", "name": "router", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_normal.png?m=1588961795", "title": "路由器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/router", "topics": 2141, "footer": "", "header": "数据包流动的乐趣", "title_alternative": "Router", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_mini.png?m=1588961795", "stars": 2392, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 824, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 718049, "username": "bingoso", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/bingoso", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad6f/6f62/718049_mini.png?m=1769470203", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad6f/6f62/718049_normal.png?m=1769470203", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad6f/6f62/718049_large.png?m=1769470203", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ad6f/6f62/718049_xlarge.png?m=1769470203", "created": 1730446006, "last_modified": 1769470203, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Hugehard", "last_touched": 1772509732, "title": "你的路由器不间断运行多久了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1195155", "created": 1772427751, "deleted": 0, "content": "无意看到知乎一个问答 [每天重启路由器有好处还是有害？]  https://www.zhihu.com/question/392412428/answer/1772992455?share_code=VerCUmrwuWLY&utm_psn=2011784588310115802\r\n\r\n引用高赞的一个回答：\r\n```\r\n所以我的建议是，光猫和路由器每周重启一次。如果遇到不重启，isp 换 ip 时断网，那就每天重启一次。\r\n```\r\n\r\n可根据我的使用经验来看，除了小区断电，就没有主动重启过路由器或者光猫。当然，折腾 openwrt 时除外。\r\n\r\n![img]( https://i.imgur.com/2JfwuEU.png)", "content_rendered": "<p>无意看到知乎一个问答 [每天重启路由器有好处还是有害？]  <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/392412428/answer/1772992455?share_code=VerCUmrwuWLY&amp;utm_psn=2011784588310115802\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/392412428/answer/1772992455?share_code=VerCUmrwuWLY&amp;utm_psn=2011784588310115802</a></p>\n<p>引用高赞的一个回答：</p>\n<pre><code>所以我的建议是，光猫和路由器每周重启一次。如果遇到不重启，isp 换 ip 时断网，那就每天重启一次。\n</code></pre>\n<p>可根据我的使用经验来看，除了小区断电，就没有主动重启过路由器或者光猫。当然，折腾 openwrt 时除外。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2JfwuEU.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1772427751, "replies": 80, "id": 1195155}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10213, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2185, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 120812, "username": "sun1992", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sun1992", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a05b160b6a1bd48368d0351137e8b471?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a05b160b6a1bd48368d0351137e8b471?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a05b160b6a1bd48368d0351137e8b471?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1433517865, "last_modified": 1767750710, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "wegbjwjm", "last_touched": 1772509621, "title": "墓地也太贵了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1195184", "created": 1772433145, "deleted": 0, "content": "父母年纪大了，过年期间去打听了下墓地的价格，竟然要 8 万一个，真的买不起啊。", "content_rendered": "<p>父母年纪大了，过年期间去打听了下墓地的价格，竟然要 8 万一个，真的买不起啊。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1772437681, "replies": 74, "id": 1195184}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/nav