-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1751718333", "stars": 4465, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 687486, "username": "toriagpiosk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/toriagpiosk", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/46b933a51fb5b102f54076873ef5a495?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/46b933a51fb5b102f54076873ef5a495?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/46b933a51fb5b102f54076873ef5a495?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1714367772, "last_modified": 1714367772, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "yuruizhe", "last_touched": 1772509409, "title": "微信是如何识别远程控制环境的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1195332", "created": 1772496570, "deleted": 0, "content": "我平时经常需要远程到他人电脑上协助处理问题，但发现一个比较稳定的现象：只要在远程会话中操作微信客户端，基本都会触发“环境异常”，随后被强制下线，几乎是 100% 复现。\r\n\r\n从这个表现来看，微信客户端应该具备一定的运行环境识别能力。比如，它是否会检测当前系统的会话类型？是否会枚举系统进程，识别是否存在远程控制软件？又或者是通过分析操作环境特征，比如鼠标轨迹、点击节奏等行为数据进行综合判断？\r\n\r\n我自己也做过一些简单排查，但并没有发现异常或特殊接口调用，所以有些困惑它具体是通过什么方式实现这一判断的。", "content_rendered": "<p>我平时经常需要远程到他人电脑上协助处理问题，但发现一个比较稳定的现象：只要在远程会话中操作微信客户端，基本都会触发“环境异常”，随后被强制下线，几乎是 100% 复现。</p>\n<p>从这个表现来看，微信客户端应该具备一定的运行环境识别能力。比如，它是否会检测当前系统的会话类型？是否会枚举系统进程，识别是否存在远程控制软件？又或者是通过分析操作环境特征，比如鼠标轨迹、点击节奏等行为数据进行综合判断？</p>\n<p>我自己也做过一些简单排查，但并没有发现异常或特殊接口调用，所以有些困惑它具体是通过什么方式实现这一判断的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1772496570, "replies": 51, "id": 1195332}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_large.png?m=1643850384", "name": "mmm", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_normal.png?m=1643850384", "title": "买买买", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mmm", "topics": 1225, "footer": "", "header": "如果你最近买了某个有点点奢侈，但是又非常酷的东西，那就发到这个节点来交（xia）流（du）一下吧", "title_alternative": "Buy Buy Buy", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_mini.png?m=1643850384", "stars": 618, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 804, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 282637, "username": "Felix96", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Felix96", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78f1/b223/282637_mini.png?m=1772500636", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78f1/b223/282637_normal.png?m=1772500636", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78f1/b223/282637_large.png?m=1772500636", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78f1/b223/282637_xlarge.png?m=1772500636", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/78f1/b223/282637_xxlarge.png?m=1772500636", "created": 1515925645, "last_modified": 1772500636, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "vegeta2ex", "last_touched": 1772510562, "title": "洗烘一体机怎么选？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1195346", "created": 1772500940, "deleted": 0, "content": "租房没有配，今年深圳梅雨天比较多，想买带烘干的，各位彭于晏们有什么推荐吗？\r\n预算 2k 以内", "content_rendered": "租房没有配，今年深圳梅雨天比较多，想买带烘干的，各位彭于晏们有什么推荐吗？<br />预算 2k 以内", "last_modified": 1772501008, "replies": 49, "id": 1195346}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 30311, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3288, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 567799, "username": "Litchi824", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Litchi824", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4c53/0b69/567799_mini.png?m=1772429014", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4c53/0b69/567799_normal.png?m=1772429014", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4c53/0b69/567799_large.png?m=1772429014", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4c53/0b69/567799_xlarge.png?m=1772429014", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4c53/0b69/567799_xxlarge.png?m=1772429014", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4c53/0b69/567799_xxxlarge.png?m=1772429014", "created": 1641191048, "last_modified": 1772429014, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "JoshTheLegend", "last_touched": 1772467024, "title": "ios 端的 tg 是被限速了吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1195162", "created": 1772430465, "deleted": 0, "content": "我有三台设备\r\n- iPhone (air/16pro/14pro)\r\n- Android (vivo/小米)\r\n- MacBook air\r\n\r\n在同一 WiFi & 同一节点的情况下, \r\n在 tg 点开视频的话, 加载速度肉眼可见的 Android ≈ MacBook(mac 还是会比 Android 慢点不过可以忍受) >> iOS,\r\n尝试过换节点, 换第三方客户端, ios 都是一样慢~\r\n\r\nso, 有哥们知道原因吗, 难道要开 tg 的会员?", "content_rendered": "<p>我有三台设备</p>\n<ul>\n<li>iPhone (air/16pro/14pro)</li>\n<li>Android (vivo/小米)</li>\n<li>MacBook air</li>\n</ul>\n<p>在同一 WiFi &amp; 同一节点的情况下,\n在 tg 点开视频的话, 加载速度肉眼可见的 Android ≈ MacBook(mac 还是会比 Android 慢点不过可以忍受) &gt;&gt; iOS,\n尝试过换节点, 换第三方客户端, ios 都是一样慢~</p>\n<p>so, 有哥们知道原因吗, 难道要开 tg 的会员?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1772430465, "replies": 39, "id": 1195162}]